I want to use the newest Selenium with facebook/php-webdriver.

### WebDriverCurlException (Actual behavior)
But I get this error in the browser targetting my PHP file:
`Uncaught exception 'Facebook\WebDriver\Exception\WebDriverCurlException' with message 'Curl error thrown for http POST to /session`. How can I fix this behavior?

I runned Selenium with the Geckodriver 16.1 provided, with these command:

